[SPEAKER_00] There is a lot of work, really, a lot of work to be done

3437
01:41:19,199 --> 01:41:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ladies and gentlemen, the next few years will be crucial for Croatia, for Slovakia, for Europe as a whole

3438
01:41:30,199 --> 01:41:33,199
